us/2068208837849420062", "text": "#China's exports of fuel oil, mainly for low-sulphur marine fuel bunkering,  totalled 1.76 million metric tons, or about 360,695 barrels per day (bpd) in Max, up 4% from April, according to General Administration of Customs data #oott https://t.co/BxC375LpNM", "time": "05:46", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 2698, "likes": 11, "replies": 0, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068222827879178665", "url": "https://x.com/TheWuhanClan/status/2068222827879178665", "text": "Weekend Wall Streer starting to sell off over the negative Iran deal news 🚩🚩 $es $spy #oott $vix", "time": "06:42", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 508, "likes": 2, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068226046919418240", "url": "https://x.com/TheWuhanClan/status/2068226046919418240", "text": "BREAKING:  Israel killed another 5 in Lebanon despite Trump’s demand for a ceasefire to preserve Iran deal 🚩 #oott $es $spy $btc $eth $sol $vix", "time": "06:54", "author": "TheWuhanClan", "author_name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "views": 435, "likes": 4, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068229169721245883", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068229169721245883", "text": "Hormuz Reopening Shifts Focus to Gulf Oil Storage and Shipping\nShipowners need to regain confidence in the route, insurers need to lower premiums and producers need to load crude quickly enough to avoid bottlenecks\n#oott https://t.co/jTkfNGF6lg", "time": "07:07", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 2701, "likes": 15, "replies": 0, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068258204987859288", "url": "https://x.com/Riccardino999/status/2068258204987859288", "text": "#aet #afentra #oott\n\nNext two weeks we should have the results for the Pacassa SW drill\n\nThe major risk now is geology, with 60% chance of success.\n\nThe drill is in an untapped extension delimited by a clear structural fault that could have been filled by the same kitchen below https://t.co/zWW79mbL", "time": "09:02", "author": "Riccardino999", "author_name": "Mr Rhino", "followers": 1449, "views": 3167, "likes": 14, "replies": 2, "retweets": 1, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068265519040348629", "url": "https://x.com/SpreadChartsCom/status/2068265519040348629", "text": "Maybe I’m blind 👀, but I don’t see the record Brent 🛢️ short positions everyone is freaking out about 🤔\n\nYes, speculative net positions have collapsed 📉\n\nBut most speculators are still net long 📊 (net traders), and retail remains fully invested ⚠️\n\n#OOTT $BNO $USO $XLE $XOP https://t.co/CvjVup6bao", "time": "09:31", "author": "SpreadChartsCom", "author_name": "SpreadCharts.com", "followers": 4362, "views": 1156, "likes": 10, "replies": 3, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068282817004314706", "url": "https://x.com/piotrmiecz/status/2068282817004314706", "text": "Jeszcze miesiąc \"pokoju\" i braku ropy z bliskiego wschodu i zacznie się gigantyczny kryzys paliwowy.\n\nDane: Morgan Stanley\n\n#oott https://t.co/veCgZHKkz2", "time": "10:40", "author": "piotrmiecz", "author_name": "Piotr Mieczkowski TMT", "followers": 4099, "views": 1097, "likes": 11, "replies": 2, "retweets": 2, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068302401937801495", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068302401937801495", "text": "China's May refined oil exports rise from April under restrictions, Australia receives agreed volume #oott https://t.co/9YVUpEkOgD", "time": "11:58", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 2966, "likes": 18, "replies": 0, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068307749495070817", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2068307749495070817", "text": "WTI futures are over-sold\n\nPrice fell $8.28 (10%) from $84.99 to $76.60 week ending June 19\n\n12-month spreads suggest sideways prices on Monday\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/ZLAGhWcZH0", "time": "12:19", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 4333, "likes": 43, "replies": 8, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068308934868242913", "url": "https://x.com/aeberman12/status/2068308934868242913", "text": "WTI  12-month spread narrowed $4.31 (38%) for the week ending June 19\n\n6-month spread narrowed $3.36 (45%) \n\nPrice fell $8.28 (10%) from $84.88 to $76.60\n#energy #OOTT #oilandgas #WTI #CrudeOil #fintwit #OPEC #Commodities #commoditiesmarket https://t.co/zAFMoJM0ys", "time": "12:24", "author": "aeberman12", "author_name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "views": 2216, "likes": 17, "replies": 1, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068321067312062692", "url": "https://x.com/ZmansEnrgyBrain/status/2068321067312062692", "text": "#OOTT", "time": "13:12", "author": "ZmansEnrgyBrain", "author_name": "Z4 Energy Research", "followers": 11920, "views": 1417, "likes": 4, "replies": 3, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068322912902258894", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068322912902258894", "text": "Iran's Tasnim report Strait of Hormuz closed due to ceasefire violation #oott", "time": "13:19", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3230, "likes": 23, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068323382915940543", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068323382915940543", "text": "\"Strait of Hormuz will be closed to all maritime traffic\" #oott", "time": "13:21", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 4841, "likes": 28, "replies": 1, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 4, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068324249647943785", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068324249647943785", "text": "The boss of #Iraq’s state oil-marketing company SOMO, Ali Nizar, said separately in an interview with Iraq 24 television that two ships are currently loading at the country’s southern terminal but that more would need to enter Hormuz for output to keep rising.\n#oott", "time": "13:25", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 3694, "likes": 14, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068351287423320555", "url": "https://x.com/cbjom/status/2068351287423320555", "text": "I guess Team Iran has come to negotiate on everything  other than nukes.\n\n#OOTT", "time": "15:12", "author": "cbjom", "author_name": "Crudehead🛢", "followers": 17544, "views": 2732, "likes": 8, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068379950269252046", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2068379950269252046", "text": "IEA on SPR releases :\nApril release pace 2mbpd, May pace 2.5mbpd,\n252mb so far released, further scheduled releases 79mb\n #oott https://t.co/XMXilk4l6h", "time": "17:06", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 34617, "likes": 75, "replies": 7, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 21, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068397928260284736", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2068397928260284736", "text": "Here is the SAR satellite imagery of the SoH dated June 20th. Zoom in and those white specks are your hulls. The traditional transit lanes are zero traffic. Every single ship on the tape is currently hugging the Iranian corridor.\n\n#oott #iran https://t.co/gLBdvWNY1g", "time": "18:17", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 46590, "likes": 215, "replies": 17, "retweets": 29, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 22, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068404791219495210", "url": "https://x.com/CRUDEOIL231/status/2068404791219495210", "text": "Oil exports are strictly a winner's game. \n\nOther GCC players can't even get normal loadings off the ground today, but Iran is out here concurrently loading three hulls over at Kharg. \n\nThen again, they're already on track to pocket tens of billions of dollars anyway!\n\n#oott #iran", "time": "18:45", "author": "CRUDEOIL231", "author_name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "views": 29403, "likes": 280, "replies": 11, "retweets": 33, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 17, "labels": null}, {"id": "2068430632192004138", "url": "https://x.com/jackprandelli/status/2068430632192004138", "text": "the link for the full article is here: \n\n https://t.co/Pi4KvODDpi\n\n#oott", "time": "20:27", "author": "jackprandelli", "author_name": "Jack Prandelli", "followers": 46547, "views": 1550, "likes": 7, "replies": 0, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": null}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 7, "views": 54747, "likes": 184}, {"username": "TheWuhanClan", "name": "Wuhan Fourth Turning Swan", "followers": 20042, "tweets": 6, "views": 2576, "likes": 17}, {"username": "PMroil", "name": "Phil MrOil", "followers": 611, "tweets": 4, "views": 2820, "likes": 13}, {"username": "CDCapMan", "name": "CD Capital Management", "followers": 164, "tweets": 4, "views": 1390, "likes": 9}, {"username": "aeberman12", "name": "Art Berman", "followers": 53616, "tweets": 2, "views": 6549, "likes": 60}], "top_authors_by_views": [{"username": "CRUDEOIL231", "name": "JH", "followers": 59314, "tweets": 2, "views": 75993, "likes": 495}, {"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "tweets": 7, "views": 54747, "likes": 184},